1206
01:20:32,744 --> 01:20:35,454
Three kinds of meat in the meatballs:

1207
01:20:35,622 --> 01:20:37,665
veal, beef, and pork.

1208
01:20:38,041 --> 01:20:40,125
Good, but you gotta have the pork.

1209
01:20:40,293 --> 01:20:41,836
That's the flavor.

1210
01:20:42,003 --> 01:20:45,464
I felt he used too many onions,
but it was still a very good sauce.

1211
01:20:45,632 --> 01:20:48,425
Vinnie, don't put too many onions
in the sauce.

1212
01:20:48,593 --> 01:20:51,178
I didn't put too much onions in, Paul.

1213
01:20:51,471 --> 01:20:53,264
Put three small onions, that's all I did.

1214
01:20:53,431 --> 01:20:55,975
Three onions? How many cans
