1216
01:20:59,062 --> 01:21:01,063
Johnny Dio did the meat.

1217
01:21:01,231 --> 01:21:03,816
We had no broiler,
so Johnny did everything in pans.

1218
01:21:03,984 --> 01:21:06,110
It used to smell up the joint
