1219
01:21:06,278 --> 01:21:09,238
and the hacks used to die,
but he still cooked a great steak.

1220
01:21:09,406 --> 01:21:11,949
- How do you like yours?
- Medium rare.

1221
01:21:12,534 --> 01:21:14,660
Medium rare. An aristocrat.

1222
01:21:15,078 --> 01:21:18,831
You know, when you think
of prison you get pictures in your mind...

1223
01:21:18,999 --> 01:21:22,626
of all those old movies
with rows of guys behind bars.

1224
01:21:22,794 --> 01:21:24,712
It wasn't like that for wiseguys.

1225
01:21:24,880 --> 01:21:27,548
It really wasn't that bad,
excepting that I missed Jimmy...

1226
01:21:27,716 --> 01:21:29,133
who was doing his time in Atlanta.

1227
01:21:29,301 --> 01:21:31,802
Give me two steaks
while you're in there, all right?

1228
01:21:33,138 --> 01:21:37,600
Everyone else in the joint was doing
real time, mixed together, living like pigs.

1229
01:21:37,767 --> 01:21:40,769
