1242
01:22:10,258 --> 01:22:11,759
- Scotch.
- Nice.

1243
01:22:12,761 --> 01:22:14,595
-Some red wine.
-Okay.

1244
01:22:14,930 --> 01:22:16,805
-Now we can eat.
