1366
01:29:55,264 --> 01:29:56,598
It's nice, huh?

1367
01:29:56,766 --> 01:29:58,767
Henry, come over here.
Did you and Jimmy talk?

1368
01:29:58,935 --> 01:30:01,269
I talked to him,
and he's looking into everything.

1369
01:30:01,437 --> 01:30:04,815
This'll make the Air France haul
look like goddamn peanuts.

1370
01:30:04,982 --> 01:30:07,234
-Shh! Come on.
-He's gonna do it, right?

1371
01:30:07,402 --> 01:30:09,152
I told you. He'll check everything out.

1372
01:30:09,320 --> 01:30:11,988
He's looking into it.
We'll see what happens. No promises.

1373
01:30:12,156 --> 01:30:16,326
I know. Do you understand?
